{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 65.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was no question in their mind that there was something, because this whole large area where the factories were, you could still-- when you went close by, you could still smell this toxic gas in the air.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they still, after so many years-- it was 45 44 years later-- they still couldn't grow things there, and they couldn't have cattle on the ground.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they really-- you know, really wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were wondering if we could give any information, if we have any memorabilia, or how we felt, or whatever we could, if-- they know how hard it is for us and that maybe it's impossible for many of us, but how they would appreciate it.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The goal is that we want to educate our children, people, that this should never happen again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was completely broken up, because for all these 44, 45 years, I just had to live with having this completely suppressed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess because I wanted to lead, a, quote unquote, 'normal life.' So in order to live on and, you know, work and get married and have children and bring them up and-- you just had to block this out.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't find myself capable of doing this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other hand, I just had this feeling that I have to do this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was going back and forth, torturing myself between these two extremes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I decided for the first time, I sought out a psychologist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the way, she was a Christian woman, who was extremely helpful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, tell me, and I will write it for you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was going there maybe six, eight months before it-- we gave birth to an answer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then finally, they had-- and then also this letter asked them, would you be willing eventually to come to a reunion which we are planning in a year or a year and a half or something, in this site?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in my mind, this site really didn't exist on this world-- in this world, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so then to take a trip there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyway, I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were allowed to bring someone with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were paying your full fare for a week and half of your companion's.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I took my daughter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, I must say, I had these paranoid thoughts to myself on the plane, that probably they hijack the plane and they'll put us right back underground, and nobody will ever know what happened to us, and you know.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole town was getting ready for this for a long time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had-- with the German precision and planning, you know, the whole week, the festivities were planned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they were-- everything was kosher, by the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was huge buffets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- and the local women were all baking and cooking and serving us and taking our coat and taking-- it really was kind of surreal.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had lectures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had dignitaries.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had German television and radio.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The main thing, of course, was to see each other for the first time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody-- of course, nobody recognized anybody after 45 years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a difference between being 15 or 60.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
